    "These models can be easily implemented to predict data for all countries worldwide.",
    "This study will facilitate the precise prediction of COVID-19 cases and aid in the global fight against the pandemic by developing efficient strategies for effective future forecasting.",
    "Based on the scope of this study, the objectives are as follows:",
    "• To analyze the impact of COVID-19 in the UAE and Malaysia, we used demographic and socioeconomic indicators.",
    "• To compare various deep learning models, including LSTM, bidirectional LSTM, and CNN, for predicting COVID-19 cases."
